Rare 1995 Toei Music Publishing (Japan) release of Eduard Artemyev's music and sound design for Andrei Tarkovsky's films &quot;Stalker&quot; (1979) and &quot;Zerkalo&quot; (The Mirror) (1975). This is Vol 4  in a series (of 4?). 

This release is much truer to the original recordings appearing in the films than the 1999 Electroshock (Russia) Release &quot;Solaris. The Mirror. Stalker&quot;.

